  <description><![CDATA[<p>In the heart of the exclusive Forte dei Marmi resort, Hermitage Hotel &amp; Resort provides a contemporary stay on this stylish part of the Tuscan Coast. The town’s bars and restaurants are all a quick walk away and the hotel boasts its own beach club (payable locally) where you can find sun loungers with parasols, a saltwater pool, watersports and Bambaissa restaurant that attracts locals and visitors alike with its sophisticated menu and romantic setting.</p>
<p>Having recently been refurbished, the hotel boasts contemporary guestrooms that have a cosy, home-away-from-home feel. They also have larger rooms that are perfect for families. In the grounds you’ll find a decked pool area with sun loungers, a small playground for children and the Pool Bar restaurant where you’ll find lovely terraces and fresh food made from home-grown vegetables and local produce.</p>]]></description>
